## 🐛 Bug Report

I have got problem when read excel file with chart and modify some data, then I write back. The chart is missing. This case also cause when I just read excel file with chart and write back, but it is still show the same problem.

Lib version: 4.2.1

## Steps To Reproduce

var Excel = require('exceljs');
var workbook = new Excel.Workbook();
workbook.xlsx.readFile('chartsheet.xlsx')
    .then(function() {
        var worksheet = workbook.getWorksheet(2);	
        // TODO: modify data 
        return workbook.xlsx.writeFile('newchartsheet.xlsx');
})
